{"tid":611393,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣成日心口痛","createTime":"2018-03-31T03:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T19:37:21.000Z","uid":27146,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"346d5aa4cd07b4c02e50266ef259f2dfaf73de3c","tid":611393,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"或者話係左邊胸口痛<br />\n坐又好行又好都會無啦啦痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冤冤痛好攞命<br />\n有次痛到入左醫院，又心電圖又驗血<br />\n但係又搵唔倒原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfe6848e3da3e5eb80bdb2a3d9a0b08cdb1354e","tid":611393,"uid":28769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"早幾年係咁，呢一兩年少左好多"},{"pid":"1fff4bf94ebe7ad158079200f3eb4449b775f80a","tid":611393,"uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都係咁 又係不斷進出醫院但搵唔到原因"},{"pid":"55885c88296098c91e8e12788b192c2c066a658c","tid":611393,"uid":179882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n有時覺得比火燒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又check 過無野"},{"pid":"6c06aeb04fbee814ab3bb5dbbf5b0805eb3fe8a7","tid":611393,"uid":114945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"83a1605c560330b568684483c8482e96af08eff8","tid":611393,"uid":163743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"今世都唔好做激烈運動"},{"pid":"6745ad4f7bbc2471ee1d976502241ea8f31c4961","tid":611393,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fff4bf94ebe7ad158079200f3eb4449b775f80a","tid":611393,"uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都係