0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55885c88296098c91e8e12788b192c2c066a658c","tid":611393,"uid":179882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n有時覺得比火燒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又check 過無野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"火燒似係胃酸倒流，我兩三年前試過，少食多餐戒甜後好左好多，最近腸胃炎嘔左十幾次，胃酸都嘔埋出黎，有一兩日又有種拿住拿住既感覺，可以食下梳打餅舒緩。<br />\n其實睇醫生照過心電圖排除左心臟有事，除非係極少數既隱性心臟病，唔係好大機會都係胃影響，可以search下胃心綜合症，我都俾佢困擾左一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cdfc8007454c7f23b16f3b2f87d9d5ee136e02","tid":611393,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:23:32.000Z","msg":"心絞痛前期 <br />\n我poly nursing year 2<br />\n上個sem學咗<br />\n你最好睇多幾個醫生問多幾專業人士"},{"pid":"d875ec41227daa9b93c245f3ecc12fc6afaee7ac","tid":611393,"uid":103750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"以前有<br />\n讀書個時日日唔夠訓<br />\n間唔中心口會有下拿住痛<br />\n好似係個人休養唔夠<br />\n血氣運行唔好<br />\n心臟個位唔夠血所以有時會痛<br />\n而加休息食野定時<br />\n健康返就冇咩野<br />\n唔知樓主個種痛係咪同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eb7bcc624f50777922c721a587ac1e02730e04","tid":611393,"uid":123690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9814bef963a0decf98f17b3832a69207b56d1f","tid":611393,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪成日好易就發惡 or生活壓力好 or  成日食辣野油炸野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"我係，3樣都中(食炸野)，當中有關係嗎？"},{"pid":"61970457b65c1e6eb1a868ab0f25d9786f248df3","tid":611393,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2eb7bcc624f50777922c721a587ac1e02730e04","tid":611393,"uid":123690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9814bef963a0decf98f17b3832a69207b56d1f","tid":611393,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪成日好易就發惡 or生活壓力好 or  成日食辣野油炸野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"我係，3樣都中(食炸野)，當中有關係嗎？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"係, 仲要係好有關係<br />\n<br />\n我自己都有依類問題起碼 3 年 ,  中間睇過西醫中醫<br />\n西醫搞唔掂依類問題架啦,  廢架,  啲藥只係 for 你止乜止乜,  唔會有根底既幫助<br />\n<br />\n放棄西醫之後,  我睇過幾個中醫,  主要係想聽下佢地對我病情有咩見解<br />\n直到近半年先搵到個中醫,  佢講既病因我都幾認同<br />\n<br />\n之後病情紓緩左好多"},{"pid":"175e94ebfaa0f65673fc5d226cee0ed227a6b6da","tid":611393,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"早幾年有<br />\n而家無晒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948f7e4c980b35950525d9bb931e64579082bef8","tid":611393,"uid":27210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"55cdfc8007454c7f23b16f3b2f87d9d5ee136e02","tid":611393,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:23:32.000Z","msg":"心絞痛前期 <br />\n我poly nursing year 2<br />\n上個sem學咗<br />\n你最好睇多幾個醫生問多幾專業人士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"收皮啦傻仔<br />\n人地唔信醫生信你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1939826302f642fb0c704f931023c92fb33960d","tid":611393,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71dbabac63956ab12188acc204f5f76cb39a6ba","tid":611393,"uid":163972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"太少information<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呼吸會唔會痛？<br />\n做運動會唔會痛？<br />\n多數痛幾耐好返"},{"pid":"a12f4d00faa140aba65c95f6571047b482f705e6","tid":611393,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd4ec790cb9fd1f0ca8752cdbd7eac6796d22df","tid":611393,"uid":123492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"胃酸倒流 <br />\n同樓主一樣入急症check哂血 x光 乜事都無<br />\n你會feel到個心口戚下戚下咁痛+好似抖唔到氣咁<br />\n如果係咁既話好大